name: KMV2 #004
description: KoleMozterV2 (KMV2) is a precious collection that grows day by day. Precious and Exclusive monster robots in 2D drawing, Each collection is drawing by hand with simple software, simple brush, and coloring technique. I love this KMV2 robots project because it reminds me of my childhood playing with friends with toy robots made from used goods, such as used bottles, bamboo, used cans, and used flip flops.
